},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of bullet list"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"bullet list","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBulletList"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBulletListComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BulletListComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"bullet list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Bullet list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebulletlistcomponenttokensprovider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider/spaceColumnGapBodyLarge":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider\/spaceColumnGapBodyLarge","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebulletlistcomponenttokensprovider\/spacecolumngapbodylarge","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token spaces.columnGapSmall","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spaceColumnGapBodyLarge","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","text":"SpaceSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"spaceColumnGapBodyLarge"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemeso